PN,30201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FHS2 trains will run slower than
OL,8,Foriginally planned, in an effort to
OL,9,Fkeep down rising construction costs.
OL,11,FThe Transport Secretary Heidi
OL,12,FAlexander told MPs on Tuesday that the
OL,13,Fnew maximum speed of HS2 services will
OL,14,Fbe 320km/h, down from the intended
OL,15,F360km/h (224mph).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FAlexander also confirmed the trains
OL,8,Fwould no longer be operational by the
OL,9,Fintended date of 2033, saying we could
OL,10,Finstead see the first trains on tracks
OL,11,Fas late as 2039, with trains not
OL,12,Frunning all the way to Euston until as
OL,13,Flate as 2043.
OL,15,FThe line was originally meant to open
OL,16,Fin 2026, and was initially announced
OL,17,Fin 2012 by a Conservative government,
OL,18,Fhaving been consulted on by Gordon
OL,19,FBrown's Labour government in 2009.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FSince being announced, the project has
OL,8,Frisen from an initial #32.7 billion in
OL,9,F2011 prices to #66.6 billion for just
OL,10,Fthe London to Birmingham route, having
OL,11,Fat one point topped an estimated #100
OL,12,Fbillion when stretching further north
OL,13,Fto Manchester.
OL,15,FSpeaking on Tuesday, Heidi Alexander
OL,16,Fsaid the new estimated cost for the
OL,17,Fproject sat between #87.7 billion to
OL,18,F#102.7 billion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,F"If this seems like an obscene
OL,8,Fincrease in time and costs, it's
OL,9,Fbecause it is," said Alexander.
OL,11,F"And if it seems like I'm angry, it is
OL,12,Fbecause I am."
OL,14,FSo what happened to the HS2 project,
OL,15,Fand is a high-speed railway line going
OL,16,Fslower just, well, a railway line?
OL,18,FA timeline of delays and setbacks
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FJanuary 2009 - The Labour government
OL,8,Festablishes HS2 Ltd to examine the
OL,9,Fcase for a new high-speed rail line.
OL,11,FJanuary 2012 - Transport secretary
OL,12,FJustine Greening announces the
OL,13,Fgovernment has decided to go ahead
OL,14,Fwith the project, which is expected to
OL,15,Fcost #32.7 billion (in 2011 prices) `
OL,16,Fplus #8.2 billion for the trains ` and
OL,17,Fopen in 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FJune 2013 - The government raises the
OL,8,Fexpected cost of HS2 excluding rolling
OL,9,Fstock to #42.6 billion (in 2013
OL,10,Fprices), with another #7.5 billion set
OL,11,Faside for trains, the total cost could
OL,12,Fexceed #50 billion.
OL,14,FNovember 2015 - HS2 is given a new
OL,15,Fbudget of #55.7 billion (in 2015
OL,16,Fprices) to take account of inflation.
OL,18,FJune 2016 - The National Audit Office
OL,19,Fwarns HS2 is under financial strain
OL,20,Fand could be delayed by a year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FJuly 2019 - An internal review warns
OL,8,Fcosts could overrun by as much as #30
OL,9,Fbillion.
OL,11,FJanuary 2020 - A government-
OL,12,Fcommissioned report led by former HS2
OL,13,FLtd chairman Douglas Oakervee is
OL,14,Fwidely leaked. It finds HS2 could cost
OL,15,Fup to #106 billion, but concludes "on
OL,16,Fbalance" that the project should
OL,17,Fcontinue.
OL,26,@wD@cOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FFebruary 2020 - Then prime minister
OL,8,FBoris Johnson gives HS2 the go-ahead
OL,9,Fdespite "exploded" costs. The budget
OL,10,Ffor phase one between London and
OL,11,FBirmingham is set at #44.6 billion (at
OL,12,F2019 prices), with the estimated cost
OL,13,Ffor the full network revised to a
OL,14,Frange of #72 billion-#98 billion.
OL,15,FServices are expected to begin between
OL,16,F2029 and 2033.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FMarch 2020 - Environmentalist Chris
OL,8,FPackham launches a legal challenge,
OL,9,Fclaiming the project would disrupt
OL,10,Fhundreds of important environmental
OL,11,Fsites.
OL,13,FSeptember 2020 - Boris Johnson marks
OL,14,Fthe project's formal beginning of
OL,15,Fconstruction at an event in Solihull,
OL,16,FWest Midlands.
OL,18,FNovember 2021 - HS2's eastern leg
OL,19,Fbetween Leeds and the East Midlands is
OL,20,Fscrapped by the government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FMarch 2023 - Work at Euston is paused
OL,8,Fby the government as costs have
OL,9,Fballooned to #4.8 billion compared
OL,10,Fwith an initial budget of #2.6
OL,11,Fbillion. This means HS2 services will
OL,12,Frun to and from Old Oak Common, west
OL,13,FLondon, until at least the 2040s.
OL,14,FConstruction of the Birmingham to
OL,15,FCrewe leg is also delayed by two years.
OL,17,FOctober 2023 - Then prime minister
OL,18,FRishi Sunak announces at the
OL,19,FConservative Party conference that HS2
OL,20,Fwill not go beyond the West Midlands
OL,21,Fto save money.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FJanuary 2024 - HS2 Ltd executive
OL,8,Fchairman Sir Jon Thompson tells MPs
OL,9,Fthe estimated cost of building HS2
OL,10,Fbetween London and Birmingham has
OL,11,Fincreased to as much as #66.6 billion
OL,12,Fin current prices.
OL,14,FJune 2025 - Transport Secretary Heidi
OL,15,FAlexander says there is "no route" to
OL,16,Fmeet the target date of HS2 opening by
OL,17,F2033.
OL,26,@wD@YOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
