OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FMay 2026 - Alexander announces trains
OL,8,Fwill run slower to reduce costs,
OL,9,Fsetting out a new timeline for when
OL,10,Fthe line will be operational and
OL,11,Fupdating that costs could reach as
OL,12,Fhigh as #102.2 billion.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FDoes speed matter?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FOn Tuesday, Alexander confirmed to
OL,8,FMPs, the top speed of HS2 trains would
OL,9,Fbe reduced from 360 km/h to 320 km/h
OL,10,Fin efforts to reduce the cost of the
OL,11,Finfrastructure project.
OL,13,FThe reduction in speed would allow the
OL,14,Ftrains to be tested on existing tracks
OL,15,Fin the UK without the need to
OL,16,Fconstruct bespoke rail or wait for the
OL,17,Fwhole route to be finished - something
OL,18,Fthat would create further delays and
OL,19,Fcosts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FMost high-speed trains in this country
OL,8,Frun at up to 200 km/h, while those on
OL,9,Fthe Channel Tunnel Rail Link (HS1)
OL,10,Foperate at up to 300 km/h.
OL,12,FDespite the slower speed, this is
OL,13,Fstill faster than some global
OL,14,Fcomparisons like Japan's bullet
OL,15,Ftrains, which reach up to 285 km/h,
OL,16,Fthough covers a far greater distance
OL,17,Fof nearly 3,000 km.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FTrains running from London to
OL,8,FBirmingham currently take between one
OL,9,Fhour 16 minutes to two hours, covering
OL,10,Fa distance of approximately 162 km.
OL,12,FHS2 trains were initially intended to
OL,13,Fcomplete this journey in 49 minutes;
OL,14,Fat this slower speed, it could push
OL,15,Ftimes to 55 minutes.
OL,17,FBackers of the project argue HS2's
OL,18,Fmain purpose was to increase capacity
OL,19,Fon the rail network, with faster
OL,20,Fjourneys being an added bonus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FComparisons are drawn with UK
OL,8,Fmotorways, which operate with a 70 mph
OL,9,Fspeed limit, just 10 higher than other
OL,10,FUK roads, but vastly increase capacity
OL,11,Fand the number of vehicles which can
OL,12,Ftravel, freeing up smaller roads for
OL,13,Fother types of journey.
OL,15,FHow much has the cost risen?
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, Heidi Alexander confirmed
OL,18,Fthe latest estimate for the cost of
OL,19,FHS2 could be as high as #102.2 billion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FWhen initially announced in 2011, HS2
OL,8,Fwas given an estimated cost of #32.7
OL,9,Fbillion for the entire route from
OL,10,FLondon to Birmingham, and then on to
OL,11,FManchester and Leeds.
OL,13,FAccounting for inflation, this is
OL,14,Froughly equal to #50 billion in 2026.
OL,16,FIn 2013, this estimate rose by around
OL,17,F#17 billion and then a further #6
OL,18,Fbillion in 2015.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FA report in 2019 warned these costs
OL,8,Frisked hitting #88 billion, with a
OL,9,Ffurther warning in 2020 that this
OL,10,Fcould reach as high as #100 billion.
OL,12,FWhen the Sunak government cancelled
OL,13,Fthe second leg of HS2, confirming
OL,14,Ftrains would stop at Birmingham, this
OL,15,Freduced costs substantially.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FAlexander's confirmation that the
OL,8,Flatest cost estimates sat higher than
OL,9,Fthe cost of sending Nasa's Artemis
OL,10,Frocket to the moon, will leave
OL,11,Fquestions over why the British public
OL,12,Fis paying nearly the same amount for
OL,13,Fless than half the route.
OL,15,FReasons for ballooning costs are
OL,16,Fseparated, mostly into four camps.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FSince its inception, the scope of the
OL,8,Fproject has changed in numerous ways,
OL,9,Fsome of these accounting for
OL,10,Fobjections from residents and campaign
OL,11,Fgroups, one example being the
OL,12,Flengthening of a tunnel through the
OL,13,FChilterns, and another being the
OL,14,Fconstruction of a curved shelter to
OL,15,Fprotect bats near Sheephouse Wood.
OL,17,FGround conditions were also discovered
OL,18,Fto be far worse than initially
OL,19,Fanticipated, necessitating greater
OL,20,Fpreparatory work before construction
OL,21,Fof the rail could begin.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30221
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779225068
OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FCosts have also increased on account
OL,8,Fof high inflation, and what has been
OL,9,Fdescribed by some as an overly
OL,10,Foptimistic approach to estimating
OL,11,Ftotals.
OL,13,FSpeaking on Tuesday, Alexander told
OL,14,FMPs cancelling the project would now
OL,15,Fbe almost as expensive as completing
OL,16,Fit.
OL,18,FHow lengthy is the delay?
OL,20,FWe will not see operational HS2 trains
OL,21,Funtil somewhere between 2036 and 2039.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/23
