OL,3,CHS2: Spiralling costs, slower trains,
OL,4,Cless than half the size - what went
OL,5,Cwrong?
OL,7,FShe went on to say: "Previous prime
OL,8,Fministers, in my view, created the
OL,9,Fworld's most expensive slow motion car
OL,10,Fcrash," pinning the mismanagement on
OL,11,Fconsecutive Tory leaders.Her statement
OL,12,Fon Tuesday comes after a "reset" of
OL,13,Fthe infrastructure project last year,
OL,14,Fand an attempt to act on this promise
OL,15,Fto "sort it out".
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
